u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ΘΟεοῖς\">&lt;Θ&gt;(εοῖς)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\">Κ(ατακθονίοις)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία Δομιτία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία\">Ἰουλία\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δομιτία\">Δομιτία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ζ´\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan data-text=\"μῆνας\">μῆνας\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">γ´\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἡμέρας\">ἡμέρας\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε´\u003C/span>. \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Γονεῖς\">Γονεῖς\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησαλν\">ἐποίησ&lt;α&gt;ν\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Θ | l.4 α\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ΘΟεοῖς\">Ο\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία Δομιτία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία\">ΙΟΥΛΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δομιτία\">ΔΟΜΙΤΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ζ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μῆνας\">ΜΗΝΑΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Γ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἡμέρας\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Γονεῖς\">ΓΟΝΕΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησαλν\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΛΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Θ | l.4 α\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001304_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001304_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001304.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001304-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>lapis: Ο\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 3\">line.3: \u003Cspan>lapis: ΕΠΟΙΗΣΛΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>To the underworld spirits. Iulia Domitia lived for 7 years, 3 months, and 5 days. Her parents made this.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Agli Dei inferi. Giulia Domizia visse sette anni, tre mesi, cinque giorni. I suoi genitori realizzarono questo.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The structure of the epitaph is the most common for pagan epitaphs, with the invocation to the underworld spirits, the name of the deceased in nominative and his/her age, the names of the dedicant (in this case, the parents, who are not named, see also IG 14.483 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001306\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001306\u003C/a>) and the dedication verb in the aorist form (Korhonen 2004: 85-86). The \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">nomen\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Δομιτία\u003C/span> from the \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">gens Domitia\u003C/span> may have spread especially since the reign of Nero: from prosopography and palaeography, therefore, the inscription can be dated from the mid-1st century CE to the end of the 2nd century CE.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Castelli 1769 151 no. 32 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1784 159 no. 35 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 346 no. 2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Franz 1853 5704 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">481\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 98 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 85-86 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Rhomboid Ο. The letters at l. 3 are slightly larger and more spaced out than the other lines.\u003C/p>  Lines 1-4  15-22  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[268,271,274,277,280,282,285,288,291],{"id":269,"html":270},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ΘΟεοῖς\">&lt;Θ&gt;(εοῖς)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\">Κ(ατακθονίοις)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία Δομιτία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία\">Ἰουλία\u003C/span>  